room_title: Escape room "Gallery 3919" by Escapism in San Diego
room_address: 3919 4th ave Suite A, San Diego CA 92103
room_description: You've received a mysterious invitation to a private viewing at one of the most prestigious art galleries in the city. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, would be to locate a valuable artifact hidden inside the gallery. The alarms will be down for 60 minutes. Will you choose to go?
